channel.title: Feedback please
channel.description:
Hi everyone! I’ve been using Auxy for about a year now, and I’ve made a fair number of tracks that I’ve been a little shy to share. I hope I can get some feedback here, good or bad. I’m open and thick skinned so please don’t hold back. Enjoy!
This was the very first track I made on the app... https://soundcloud.app.goo.gl/AaQokj7nKLncD78k8
This is the very last track I’ve made... https://soundcloud.app.goo.gl/EACA9hb3GXBbJTJn8
Thanks!
